title: Steve Ekedi
text:
Steve Thibaut Ekedi Soppo (born 24 May 1991), known as Steve Ekedi, is a <a href="Cameroon">Cameroon</a>ian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="TORRENT%20CF">TORRENT CF</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Segunda%20Liga">Segunda Liga</a> for <a href="C.D.%20Aves">Desportivo das Aves</a> on 8 November 2015 in a game against <a href="F.C.%20Famalic%C3%A3o">Famalicão</a> and scored on his debut.
